   - Build StubArModel with TWO scripts:
     - Script 0 (first model call): emits MessageStart, then `ModelStreamEvent::ToolUseStart { id: "use_1", name: "echo" }`, then `ModelStreamEvent::ToolUseComplete { id: "use_1", name: "echo", input: serde_json::json!({"text":"hi"}) }`, then `MessageComplete { usage }`. No ContentDelta/ContentComplete events.
     - Script 1 (second model call after tool dispatch): emits MessageStart, ContentDelta "done", ContentComplete "done", MessageComplete { usage }.
   - Build Agent with registry containing EchoTool (which echoes input wrapped under "echo").
   - Send a UserMessage.
   - Drain events. Use count-RunCompletes strategy waiting for TWO RunCompletes (one per model call).
