Each of the 6 built-in tools (add, read, write, edit, insert, exec_bash) defines a byte-identical helper:

    fn err(e: <ToolErr>) -> ToolError {
        let value = serde_json::to_value(e)
            .unwrap_or_else(|_| serde_json::json!({"kind": "internal_error"}));
